settings.left_text: Tight clothes can be constricting and uncomfortable, leading to increased stress and anxiety. Loose clothes, on the other hand, can promote relaxation and ease tension.
Loose clothes provide more freedom of movement and flexibility, which can be important during physical activity or exercise.
It allow for a greater range of motion, making them a good choice for activities such as yoga or dance, where flexibility and freedom of movement are important.

settings.right_text: Loose clothes allow for increased air flow and decreased restriction, which can lead to improved comfort, especially during hot weather or physical activity.
Tight-fitting clothes can cause skin irritation or chafing, while loose clothes can help prevent these issues by reducing friction.
Loose clothes can help people feel more comfortable and confident in their own skin, especially if they are self-conscious about their body shape or size.
